<P>
MOUNTAIN LIONS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Re "Too Close to Home," Sept. 6, concerning the mountain lions: 
</P>
<P>
 As population explosion and developers' greed keep encroaching upon the domain 
of the lion, the lion is always the loser. The state is inept in any leeffort 
to curtail development and protect our wildlife.California is rapidly becoming 
a disgusting place to live.  
</P>
