games of the NFL season: 06,12,05,05,07,05,04 Opp. Com Att Yds Int TD Miami 32 
51 421 2 4 Buffalo 26 42 380 2 3 Cincinnati 30 50 365 2 1 Total 88 143 1,166 6 
8  
</P>
