<HEADLINE>
<P>
WEST VENTURA COUNTY FOCUS: CAMARILLO; CHAMBER TO EXTEND HOURS ON SATURDAYS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By J.E. MITCHELL 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 In order to meet an increasing demand for service, the Camarillo Chamber of 
Commerce will expand its weekday office hours to include Saturdays, officials 
said. 
</P>
<P>
 Beginning next month, the chamber office at 632 Las Posas Road will be open 
Saturdays from 10 a.m. to 2 p.m., said chamber executive director Carol 
Nordahl. 
</P>
<P>
 "We have had numerous requests for information from people who are considering 
relocating here," Nordahl said. "We want to provide them with information on 
Saturdays that will be helpful to them." 
</P>
<P>
 Nordahl said the new schedule will be conducted on a trial basis through Nov. 
19. 
</P>
<P>
 For more information on the chamber, call 484-4383. J.E. MITCHELL 
</P>
</TEXT>
