<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA091994-0190 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 080782 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
September 19, 1994, Monday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Part A; Page 3; Column 4; Metro Desk 
</P>
